description:
This is another fork to the canyon named First Chance Canyon

Approach

Descent

This canyon has two sections that are vertical walls of 300' & over. But both walls were split into two rappels each by finding secondary rap anchors on the way down. But could be done as long drops with one rope if the group wanted to do it that way
